---
import {
  Card,
  CardContent,
  CardDescription,
  CardHeader,
  CardTitle,
} from "../lib/shadcn-imports";
import { Badge } from "../lib/shadcn-imports";
import { Star } from "../lib/shadcn-imports";
---

<section class="py-32 px-8 md:px-16 bg-primary-black text-primary">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="mb-24 space-y-6 lazy-appear fade-up">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="jp-dot"></div>
        <span class="text-xs text-muted font-light tracking-widest uppercase"
          >Testimonios</span
        >
      </div>
      <h2
        class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extralight text-primary jp-title max-w-3xl"
      >
        Experiencias reales
      </h2>
      <div class="w-32 h-px bg-gold/40"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials grid with asymmetric spacing -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-x-8 gap-y-16">
      <div class="space-y-8 group lazy-appear fade-up">
        <div class="flex gap-1">
          {
            Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_, i) => (
              <Star
                className="w-3 h-3 fill-gold/70 text-gold/70 opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                client:load
              />
            ))
          }
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted/80 font-light leading-loose">
          "Legato ha transformado mi flujo de trabajo. Documentación automática
          y contratos impecables con revisión legal por IA."
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="font-light text-primary text-base">Carlos Mendoza</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-muted/60 tracking-wider">
            Full-Stack · Bogotá
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-gold/20"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8 group md:mt-12 lazy-appear fade-up delay-100">
        <div class="flex gap-1">
          {
            Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_, i) => (
              <Star
                className="w-3 h-3 fill-jade/70 text-jade/70 opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                client:load
              />
            ))
          }
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted/80 font-light leading-loose">
          "Contratos profesionales adaptados a legislación colombiana. El envío
          automático por WhatsApp es perfecto."
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="font-light text-primary text-base">Ana López</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-muted/60 tracking-wider">
            Backend · Medellín
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-jade/20"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8 group lazy-appear fade-up delay-200">
        <div class="flex gap-1">
          {
            Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_, i) => (
              <Star
                className="w-3 h-3 fill-blue-gray/70 text-blue-gray/70 opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                client:load
              />
            ))
          }
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted/80 font-light leading-loose">
          "Dashboard con estadísticas claras que me ayudan a optimizar tarifas y
          tomar decisiones informadas sobre mi negocio."
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="font-light text-primary text-base">Juan Pérez</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-muted/60 tracking-wider">Mobile · Cali</div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-blue-gray/20"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8 group lazy-appear fade-up delay-100">
        <div class="flex gap-1">
          {
            Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_, i) => (
              <Star
                className="w-3 h-3 fill-gold/70 text-gold/70 opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                client:load
              />
            ))
          }
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted/80 font-light leading-loose">
          "Todo automatizado y profesional. Odio los papeleos y Legato los
          elimina por completo. Clientes impresionados."
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="font-light text-primary text-base">María García</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-muted/60 tracking-wider">
            Frontend · Barranquilla
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-gold/20"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8 group md:mt-12 lazy-appear fade-up delay-200">
        <div class="flex gap-1">
          {
            Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_, i) => (
              <Star
                className="w-3 h-3 fill-jade/70 text-jade/70 opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                client:load
              />
            ))
          }
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted/80 font-light leading-loose">
          "IA para documentación espectacular. Diagramas y requisitos en
          minutos. Antes tardaba días en documentación técnica."
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="font-light text-primary text-base">Diego Ruiz</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-muted/60 tracking-wider">
            Architect · Bucaramanga
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-jade/20"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8 group lazy-appear fade-up delay-300">
        <div class="flex gap-1">
          {
            Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_, i) => (
              <Star
                className="w-3 h-3 fill-blue-gray/70 text-blue-gray/70 opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                client:load
              />
            ))
          }
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted/80 font-light leading-loose">
          "Escalé mi negocio freelance gracias a Legato. Más proyectos sin
          sacrificar calidad. Billing excelente."
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="font-light text-primary text-base">Laura Torres</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-muted/60 tracking-wider">
            DevOps · Cartagena
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-blue-gray/20"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
